### Short Link API — REST Client examples
### Install the "REST Client" extension in VS Code, then click "Send Request" on each block.

@base = http://localhost:3000

### Create a link (auto-generated slug)
POST {{base}}/links
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "destination": "https://www.anthropic.com",
  "title": "Anthropic",
  "tags": ["ai", "docs"]
}

### Create a link with a custom slug
POST {{base}}/links
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "destination": "https://www.anthropic.com/claude",
  "slug": "claude",
  "title": "Claude product page",
  "tags": ["ai", "product"]
}

### List all links
GET {{base}}/links

### List with filters
GET {{base}}/links?tag=marketing&status=active&limit=5

### Search
GET {{base}}/links?search=google

### Filter by date range
GET {{base}}/links?from=2026-05-01&to=2026-05-31

### Sort by clicks
GET {{base}}/links?sort=clicks&order=desc&limit=5

### Get one link
GET {{base}}/links/google

### Get analytics for one link
GET {{base}}/links/google/analytics

### Get raw clicks
GET {{base}}/links/google/clicks?page=1&limit=10

### Account summary
GET {{base}}/stats/summary

### Top 5 links by clicks (all time)
GET {{base}}/stats/top?metric=clicks&period=all&limit=5

### Most recent links
GET {{base}}/stats/top?metric=recent&limit=5

### Links expiring within 14 days
GET {{base}}/links/expiring?within=14d

### All tags
GET {{base}}/tags

### Update a link
PATCH {{base}}/links/claude
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Claude — updated"
}

### Delete a link
DELETE {{base}}/links/claude

### Follow a redirect
GET {{base}}/r/google
